The paper deals with the problem of automatically extracting subroutine summary descriptions from unstructured code comments, which is a software engineering problem. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of crowdsourcing and machine learning algorithms, which are common in programming languages (cs.PL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of natural language processing (cs.CL) and provides cost estimates (cs.LG).
